You see, I just learned on the telephone at the gas station...

1046
01:07:42,400 --> 01:07:45,340
她最失策是在梳打鎮讓你下車后
that she was most indiscreet after she left you at Soda City.

1047
01:07:45,410 --> 01:07:47,340
便直接前往找當地的警長
She went to the sheriff, who,

1048
01:07:47,410 --> 01:07:49,340
