I was right about you.

1061
01:08:18,450 --> 01:08:22,390
堅尼先生  晚上好
Good evening, Mr. Kane.

1062
01:08:22,460 --> 01:08:24,400
想不到你竟是書呆子
I didn't know you were a bookworm.

1063
01:08:24,460 --> 01:08:27,470
