Once we do that, our organization is finished.

1121
01:11:14,700 --> 01:11:16,640
不惜代價  也要繼續
- We must carry on.

1122
01:11:16,710 --> 01:11:17,640
明天那件事如何  
- What about tomorrow's work ?

1123
01:11:17,710 --> 01:11:19,640
